divs: sighting detailsgwyn, thanks for this. they're certainly intriguing images. unfortunately, now that i've left the mod, i no longer have access to facilities that would enable me to analyse these images scientifically. however, you may want to pass them to the mutual ufo newtwork: http:\\www.mufon.com\ best wishes, nick pope ======================================== message received: jan 27 2009, 03:16 pm from: [cms\tg\pid] to: [cms\tg\pid] cc: subject: ufo picture fox news report - january 2009 gave me a contact to relay the following: ventura county, california solano verde ranches, somis, california listed the property @ 6868 coyote canyon drive, and borrowed pictures from a previous flyer for mls entry until my photographer was available. i placed the picture in photo shop to check the quality and noticed what looked like smudges in the upper right corner. enlarged the photo to take a look and found two objects that certainly look like our idea of ufo's. [cms\tg\pid], thousand oaks broker was the previous listing broker, she told me she knew about the flying objects in the picture on her flyer which was taken 4-5 years ago. i thought it might be of interest.
